{
  "stem": "14897.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, there was some-- not dating, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but some flirting and so on, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, in the ghetto of Warsaw, when it existed, there was a Jewish government called the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had always been-- the Jewish community had its own sort of-- not jurisdiction in Poland, but it had a-- a-- a an administrative unit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans maintained it and communicated with the Jewish populations through that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were people, Jews, who were willing to denounce other Jews to save their own lives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a little unit was formed, which was called the Jewish Gestapo, a kind of an adjunct to the German Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people survived in larger numbers the destruction of the ghetto than others, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they showed up at this Hotel Polski.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "None of them survived, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had enough confidence in the project to enlist themselves, you know, put themselves on the lists, and went with us, as it turned out, to a German camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this Hotel Polski, we were there a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, we were transported by train into what they called a staging place, which turned out the German camp of Bergen-Belsen-- B-E-R-G-E-N, dash, B-E-L-Z-E-N.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that camp was in the northwest of Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The nearest city, big city, was Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How long a trip was it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A couple of days on the train and, as a matter of fact, passenger train, of all things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the train-- I really don't remember too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, a couple of days was not really-- no, [? really, ?] it was not bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
